  <brief_title>Evaluation of Effectiveness and Safety of Xa Inhibitor for the Prevention of Stroke And Systemic Embolism in a Nationwide Cohort of Japanese Patients Diagnosed as Non-valvular Atrial Fibrillation</brief_title>
  <acronym>EXPAND</acronym>
  <official_title>Multi-center, Prospective, Non-interventional, Observational Cohort Study to Investigate Effectiveness and Safety of Rivaroxaban on Prevention of Stroke and Systemic Embolism in Patients With Non-valvular Atrial Fibrillation in Japanese Clinical Practice</official_title>
