  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The efficacy and safety of a novel oral Xa inhibitor for stroke and systemic embolism, namely
      rivaroxaban, in non-valvular atrial fibrillation patients are evaluated in Japanese clinical
      practice.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
